  <description>
Automatically creates a save when a raid or other red threat event occurs.

Includes options for:
• Enable / disable automatic saving
• Cooldown between saves. Default at 0
• Overwrite or create new save file

Compatible with RimWorld 1.6.
  </description>

  <url>https://github.com/superdizor/AutoRaidSave</url>

</ModMetaData>
